Ring UI: development environment setup

1. Install node.js

2: Install grunt-cli:

    npm install grunt -g

3. Install dependencies:

    npm install 

4. Prepare files:

    grunt

5. Start the watcher and the server:

    grunt server

=======================================

Build production files

    grunt build

Lint code with jshint:

    grunt jshint

Clean generated files:

    grunt cleanup

Uninstall dependencies:

    grunt uninstall
